/**
 * Admin i18n. The admin UI follows the store's default language, with a manual
 * override in Settings (persisted to localStorage). Ships curated EN + EU
 * majors; any locale not present (or any untranslated key) falls back to
 * English, so the app is always usable for anyone who installs it.
 *
 * Coverage is migrated key-by-key: wrap an admin string in `t("some.key")` and
 * add the key to EN (+ the other languages when available).
 */

